Citation.sAbstract: The isobaric vapor-liquid equilibrium (VLE) data for the binary systems 2-methoxyethanol + ethylbenzene, ethylbenzene + dimethyl sulfoxide (DMSO), 2-methoxyethanol + DMSO and ternary system 2-methoxyethanol + ethylbenzene + DMSO were measured at 100.00 kPa by a VLE 602 apparatus. The VLE data for all the binary and ternary systems were thermodynamically consistent, which can pass the Wisniak's L-W test.
